Class Instance

java.lang.Object
  reuo.Instance
Direct Known Subclasses:
Client
public class Instance
extends Object

A single instance of the game. Each instance contains information about statics, mobiles, and other in-game elements.

Author:
Kristpoher Ives

getElements
